## 9. Exceptions
This policy *is* the mechanism for accepting risk; policy exceptions are raised here and under `../governance/exceptions-and-waivers.md.template`. Regulatory obligations (e.g., HIPAA safeguards and breach notification) may **not** be waived by risk acceptance.

## 10. Compliance, Monitoring & Enforcement
The [Security Officer] monitors the acceptance log for expired or unauthorized acceptances and reports to management review (`../governance/management-review.md.template`). Accepting risk without proper authority, or allowing an acceptance to lapse without re-review, is a compliance violation handled per `../people/hr-security-policy.md.template`. Assessors review the log as evidence of governed risk retention.

